{
  "event.changping_battle.choice_lian_po.text": "用廉颇坚壁清野，与秦军相持。",
  "event.changping_battle.choice_negotiate.text": "遣使入秦，议和求缓。",
  "event.changping_battle.choice_zhao_kuo.text": "易将赵括，主动出击。",
  "event.changping_battle.stage_battle.text": "长平之野，秦赵两军相峙。秦将白起伏兵于谷，赵之粮道渐断；廉颇老成持重，朝中却议易将。",
  "event.counter_success_v1.counter_success_response.text": "敌之间者已为我执。或处死以儆效尤，或放归以示宽厚——王意何如？",
  "event.cultural_exchange_jixia.choice_ignore.text": "不预其事。",
  "event.cultural_exchange_jixia.choice_participate.text": "遣使观礼，馈以束帛。",
  "event.cultural_exchange_jixia.stage_jixia.text": "齐之稷下学宫，百家荟萃，列国学士争辩于堂。各国遣使观礼，亦有自荐入学者。",
  "event.discord_success_v1.discord_success_narrative.text": "敌国君臣离心，朝议沸然。我之离间渐有成效。",
  "event.drought_northern_plain.choice_respond.text": "开仓赈济，导渠引水。",
  "event.drought_northern_plain.stage_drought.text": "北地连岁不雨，禾稼枯槁，饥民南徙。郡守告急，请发常平。",
  "event.flood_yellow_river.choice_respond.text": "命有司治河，征发徭役。",
  "event.flood_yellow_river.stage_flood.text": "河决于下游，两岸沃野尽没。流民塞道，死者枕藉。",
  "event.lanling_academy_founding.xunzi_arrives.text": "荀卿自齐入楚，至兰陵。其声望素著，求于此地立学，欲传授诸子，育才以报国。",
  "event.legalist_rise_han.choice_oppose.text": "守旧制，弃法术。",
  "event.legalist_rise_han.choice_support.text": "用申子之术，整饬吏治。",
  "event.legalist_rise_han.stage_reform.text": "申不害相韩，倡刑名法术。朝中老臣以为乱礼，少壮新进则以为良策，公议未决。",
  "event.locust_disaster.choice_respond.text": "捕蝗禁迁，移民就食。",
  "event.locust_disaster.stage_locust.text": "蝗自南来，蔽日而下，所过田禾立尽。郡县告急，请王命驱之。",
  "event.lu_conquered_by_chu.choice_resist.text": "据曲阜以拒之。",
  "event.lu_conquered_by_chu.choice_surrender.text": "纳印归命，存其宗祀。",
  "event.lu_conquered_by_chu.stage_conquest.text": "楚兵北上，围鲁都曲阜。鲁国虽奉周礼，国小兵寡，难御楚锋。",
  "event.maling_battle.choice_attack.text": "效田忌之谋，伏兵马陵。",
  "event.maling_battle.choice_defend.text": "据险固守，以逸待劳。",
  "event.maling_battle.choice_negotiate.text": "遣使讲和，赂以重币。",
  "event.maling_battle.stage_battle.text": "魏将庞涓引兵伐韩，齐救之。孙膑减灶诱敌，至马陵道，山深木茂，伏弩齐发——胜负之机正在此时。",
  "event.merchant_network_bashu.choice_ignore.text": "听其自然。",
  "event.merchant_network_bashu.choice_invest.text": "出资赞助，开通栈道。",
  "event.merchant_network_bashu.stage_trade.text": "巴蜀豪商联结商路，南通滇黔，北达关中。或献策于王，请以官资助之。",
  "event.qi_recovery_from_ye_yi.choice_counterattack.text": "用田单之谋，反攻复土。",
  "event.qi_recovery_from_ye_yi.choice_rebuild.text": "守即墨，养兵待时。",
  "event.qi_recovery_from_ye_yi.stage_recovery.text": "乐毅破齐七十余城，唯莒、即墨不下。田单守即墨，募兵聚粮，国人翘首望复。",
  "event.qin_destroys_east_zhou.choice_accept.text": "迁鼎西归，礼葬周君。",
  "event.qin_destroys_east_zhou.choice_resist.text": "保周存祀，孤注一掷。",
  "event.qin_destroys_east_zhou.stage_conquest.text": "秦兵东进，围东周君于巩。九鼎将徙咸阳，宗周遗祀岌岌可危。",
  "event.qin_unification_final.choice_resist.text": "齐卒据墙，与秦决战。",
  "event.qin_unification_final.choice_surrender.text": "齐王建归命，献地纳印。",
  "event.qin_unification_final.stage_unification.text": "秦王扫六合，五国既灭，独齐独存。秦兵临淄之外，朝中议出降还是死战。",
  "event.qin_unification_han.choice_resist.text": "据新郑死守。",
  "event.qin_unification_han.choice_surrender.text": "韩王安献地归命。",
  "event.qin_unification_han.stage_conquest.text": "秦兵临颍川，韩王束手无策。新郑空虚，宗庙危殆。",
  "event.qin_xiao_seeks_talent.choice_ignore.text": "守旧法，不录新进。",
  "event.qin_xiao_seeks_talent.choice_seek.text": "下求贤令，开门延士。",
  "event.qin_xiao_seeks_talent.stage_edict.text": "秦孝公新立，思变法图强。下令于国中：宾客群臣有能出奇计强秦者，吾且尊官，与之分土。",
  "event.rumor_success_v1.rumor_success_narrative.text": "市井流言四起，敌国民心摇荡。我之谣言已起其效。",
  "event.shang_yang_reform.choice_compromise.text": "采其大略，存旧贵之利。",
  "event.shang_yang_reform.choice_delay.text": "缓行其令，徐图后计。",
  "event.shang_yang_reform.choice_implement.text": "用商鞅之法，痛裁旧族。",
  "event.shang_yang_reform.stage_reform.text": "卫鞅自魏入秦，进强国之策。秦孝公欲行其法，朝中老臣多不悦：变法将损世卿之利，民则疑而未信。",
  "event.song_conquered_by_qi.choice_resist.text": "据彭城死守。",
  "event.song_conquered_by_qi.choice_surrender.text": "宋君奔楚，宗社移祭。",
  "event.song_conquered_by_qi.stage_conquest.text": "齐湣王伐宋，破彭城，宋偃王北走。商邑遗民，各依强邻。",
  "event.spy_exposed_high_risk_v1.spy_exposed_response.text": "我之间者，败于敌境。或抵赖以保事，或承认以求贷——大王何择？",
  "event.su_qin_vertical_alliance.choice_join.text": "遣使会盟，共抗强秦。",
  "event.su_qin_vertical_alliance.choice_refuse.text": "不预其事，自图安危。",
  "event.su_qin_vertical_alliance.stage_alliance.text": "苏秦游说六国，谋合纵拒秦。诸国君臣议之：合则恐为他国所累，不合则恐为秦所并。",
  "event.su_zhang_coalition_conflict.choice_join_horizontal.text": "从张仪连横之策。",
  "event.su_zhang_coalition_conflict.choice_join_vertical.text": "从苏秦合纵之议。",
  "event.su_zhang_coalition_conflict.choice_neutral.text": "守中立，观望成败。",
  "event.su_zhang_coalition_conflict.stage_coalition.text": "苏秦张仪各执一辞——纵横之术，撕裂天下。诸侯朝秦暮楚，一纸盟约朝定夕翻。",
  "event.tian_replaces_jiang.choice_oppose.text": "守姜氏宗法，逐田氏。",
  "event.tian_replaces_jiang.choice_support.text": "顺人心，立田氏为齐侯。",
  "event.tian_replaces_jiang.stage_transition.text": "田和迁齐康公于海上，自立为齐侯，周天子命之。姜齐自此而绝，齐国宗祀易主。",
  "event.tribal_pressure_yi_qu.choice_fight.text": "出兵讨之，以扬国威。",
  "event.tribal_pressure_yi_qu.choice_negotiate.text": "和亲遣使，以缓边患。",
  "event.tribal_pressure_yi_qu.stage_pressure.text": "义渠诸戎屡犯陇西，边吏告急。或议征讨，或议羁縻——王意未决。",
  "event.usurpation_wang.usurpation_choice.text": "天下纷乱，诸侯渐僭。今我国势日盛，左右进言：宜改称号，以王自居，与天下共其威。然周礼未坠，称王恐失人望——大王何择？",
  "event.yue_conquered_by_chu.choice_resist.text": "越王无疆死战不退。",
  "event.yue_conquered_by_chu.choice_surrender.text": "纳印归楚，散其宗族。",
  "event.yue_conquered_by_chu.stage_conquest.text": "楚威王伐越，越王无疆师败被杀。越自此分崩，江南诸地多归楚有。",
  "event.yue_yi_attack_qi.choice_counterattack.text": "聚兵反击，正面御之。",
  "event.yue_yi_attack_qi.choice_defend.text": "退守临淄，固城自保。",
  "event.yue_yi_attack_qi.choice_flee.text": "弃都奔莒，徐图后举。",
  "event.yue_yi_attack_qi.stage_invasion.text": "燕将乐毅率五国之兵伐齐，连下七十余城。临淄危急，齐湣王朝议或战或避。",
  "event.zhang_yi_horizontal.choice_accept.text": "受秦之结好，从连横之议。",
  "event.zhang_yi_horizontal.choice_reject.text": "拒秦使，仍守合纵。",
  "event.zhang_yi_horizontal.stage_horizontal.text": "张仪游说列国，倡连横事秦。或以为秦近而齐远，事秦可保西陲；或以为合纵未坏，弃约则负诸侯。",
  "event.zhao_hu_fu.choice_delay.text": "缓行其议，先观民心。",
  "event.zhao_hu_fu.choice_implement.text": "颁胡服骑射之令。",
  "event.zhao_hu_fu.choice_refuse.text": "守华夏衣冠，弃胡风。",
  "event.zhao_hu_fu.stage_reform.text": "赵武灵王欲变胡服，以骑射强兵。然朝中老臣以为弃华夏衣冠，违先王之礼——议者纷纭。",
  "event.zhongshan_zhao_conflict.choice_resist.text": "中山王据灵寿死守。",
  "event.zhongshan_zhao_conflict.choice_surrender.text": "纳印归赵，散其宗社。",
  "event.zhongshan_zhao_conflict.stage_conquest.text": "赵武灵王讨中山，三战连捷。灵寿孤危，王室宗祀风雨飘摇。",
  "event.zhou_investiture_v1.request_investiture.text": "我国势已盛，威加四方。或可遣使洛邑，请周王册封以正名分；亦可暂缓不请，自守诸侯礼。大王何意？",
  "event.zhou_recognizes_three_jin.choice_accept.text": "顺天命，承认三晋为诸侯。",
  "event.zhou_recognizes_three_jin.choice_resist.text": "守礼制，拒为之命。",
  "event.zhou_recognizes_three_jin.stage_recognition.text": "周威烈王二十三年，韩、赵、魏三家分晋。周天子下诏正式承认三家为诸侯，列国朝觐于新公。",

